AddressInfo.Title: STRUM 50 kW (Astarta)
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Entrance from Nizhniy Val Street, charger is near the entrance to the underground parking, opposite to 'Furshet' grocery.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Additional parking fee - 20 UAH / hour. Parking is 1 hour free of charge with STRUM card or with a Furshet's receipt for more than 100 UAH. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.

Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8
